headline: The Lucid-Uber Robotaxi Deal: How Nvidia Will Also Benefit

On Thursday, shares of Lucid Group (NASDAQ: LCID), a Silicon Valley-based electric vehicle (EV) maker, soared more than 36% following the announcement of a premium robotaxi service deal with ride-hailing giant Uber Technologies (NYSE: UBER).

headline: Is Lucid's Reverse Stock Split a Sign of Desperation?
